# Changeset-generated per-package changelogs (the 0.1.x release convention commits zero of these;
# `changeset version` would otherwise litter untracked packages/*/CHANGELOG.md a daemon could sweep).
# Scoped to packages/* on purpose — a broad **/CHANGELOG.md would also shadow the tracked root CHANGELOG.md.
packages/*/CHANGELOG.md
